      "widgets_values": [
        "! and ? (Exclamations/Questions): Force Kokoro to raise its pitch and add conversational energy.\n... (Ellipses): Force a long, natural, 0.5-second \"breathing\" pause.\n; (Semicolons): Provide a medium pause without dropping the pitch of the voice (keeping the sentence's momentum alive).\n, (Comas): Provide a brief, natural breathing gap.\nA.I. (Phonetic spelling): Writing it with periods forces the phonemizer to speak the letters \"A\" and \"I\" distinctly instead of slurring them."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
